00:51.560 --> 00:54.040
<i>As a youthful act of defiance,
Lindsay married...</i>

00:54.120 --> 00:55.960
<i>this man.</i>

00:56.040 --> 00:58.480
<i>They moved to Boston,
where they've become celebrated...</i>

00:58.600 --> 01:00.960
<i>for their wine and cheese
fund-raisers.</i>

01:01.040 --> 01:03.160
